      <title>联合利华股东支持 ESG 改革，因抗议者扰乱会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/unilever-holders-back-esg-rowback-as-protesters-disrupt-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管多芬香皂和梦龙冰淇淋制造商的股东们批准了这些较为宽松的目标，但联合利华削减环境承诺的举动在公司年度会议上引发了抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/unilever-holders-back-esg-rowback-as-protesters-disrupt-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通用汽车的玛丽·巴拉 (Mary Barra) 对电动未来依然不畏惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/video-gm-s-mary-barra-remains-undeterred-about-an-electric-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本周的《The Circuit》节目中，艾米丽·张 (Emily Chang) 参观了汽车制造商的工厂车间，讨论了首席执行官到 2035 年打造全电动车队的雄心壮志。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/video-gm-s-mary-barra-remains-undeterred-about-an-electric-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 15:13:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AI 初创公司 Anthropic 首次推出 Claude Chatbot 作为 iPhone 应用程序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ai-startup-anthropic-debuts-claude-chatbot-as-an-iphone-app</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 的竞争对手正在更积极地推动其聊天机器人向用户提供服务，无论用户身在何处。]]></description>
